{"tid":2164144,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潔篪21日訪南韓 磋商習近平到訪時機","createTime":"2020-08-19T05:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T05:16:25.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ac1767821cd3c6d9884d206d776ff64a06f09815","tid":2164144,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:13:17.000Z","msg":"2020-08-19 12:04:00<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日前傳中共中央政治局委員、中共中央外事工作委員會辦公室主任楊潔篪將在近期拜訪南韓消息，今日，南韓青瓦台公布最新消息，確定楊潔篪將於21至22日訪問釜山，並於22日與青瓦台國家安保室長徐薰舉行會談；席間，雙方將就中國領導人習近平訪南韓事宜進行磋商，力求在武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情趨緩、時機成熟之際，促成習近平南韓行。<br />\n<br />\n根據《韓聯社》引述青瓦台發言人姜珉碩說法，楊潔篪將應徐薰之邀，於21至22日訪問釜山，並於22日同徐薰舉行會談。此為楊潔篪2018年7月後再度訪韓，同時也是武漢肺炎疫情以來首位拜訪南韓的中國高官。姜珉碩指出，楊徐2人將於22日上午舉行午餐會，就2國防疫合作、加強高層交流、朝鮮半島及國際局勢等議題交換意見。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3264762\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3264762&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInPG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=f2bd0194\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3264762&h=cdc55633\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3264762</a>"},{"pid":"778ccbd87e593f64263f548b4ab99baa762cfe2d","tid":2164144,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EM_2korWwAEBIpu.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEM_2korWwAEBIpu.jpg%3Alarge&h=2b3bd924&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79974abcdc79faf51011a406110c57dd93181509","tid":2164144,"uid":318300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:16:25.000Z","msg":"文在寅真係好Q蠢, 重諗住食两家茶禮"}]}